{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_9","type":"agent_message","text":"There’s already a session hydration field exposing asset URLs, so I’m checking whether those are storage-direct links today. If they are, I’ll replace that with backend-relative accessors and keep the asset selection rules centralized on the server side."}}
