{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_77","type":"agent_message","text":"I’ve settled the backend shape: a session-scoped asset content endpoint for concrete asset IDs, plus explicit artifact endpoints like `story-docx` that can resolve or generate the right export server-side. I’m implementing that now so the frontend can switch to backend-relative URLs and the audio player can stop talking to the emulator directly."}}
